===Etymology 1===
From {{der|az|xng|ᠵᠠᠰᠠᠭ}}, whence {{cog|mn|засаг||rule, power; law}} and {{cog|mn|засах||to fix, repair}}; ultimately from {{der|az|trk-cmn|*yasa-||determine, govern; create}}. Cognate with {{cog|tr|yasak||prohibition}}.
